oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Louis E. Trice II
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Louis E. Trice II, standing in front of a row of trees. Louis was born in Dallas, Texas to Louis E. Trice and Eura Parmer Trice in 1914. His father was born and raised in Montgomery County, Tennessee.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Trice, Louis E., II, 1914-1973
